title: OXO Tot Perfect Pull Wipes Dispenser - Gray, 1 Count (Pack of 1)
description: Keep wipes fresh, dispenses smoothly for one-handed use. Easily keep one hand on wriggly tots while using the other to grab a wipe with the PerfectPull Wipes Dispenser. The weighted plate dispenses one wipe at a time and the silicone gasket keeps wipes fresh and moist.
